@startuml sequence_product
!theme plain
title Add Hackathon Product

actor User
participant "ProductsSection" as PS
participant "AddProductDialog" as D
participant "HackathonsController" as C
participant "Handler" as H
database "DB" as DB

User -> PS: click Add Product
PS -> D: open
User -> D: fill (name, urls, members)
D -> C: POST /api/hackathons/{id}/products
C -> H: AddProductCommand
H -> DB: INSERT Product; INSERT ProductMember rows
H --> C: ProductDto
C --> D: 201
D -> PS: append card
@enduml
